tes.\nKeep Govt and tourism sites\nDeleted Commercial Sites WorldViewer.com\n-->\n* [http://kottayam.nic.in/ Official website of Kottayam District]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080423042158/http://www.ktm.kerala.gov.in/home.htm Official website from Gov. of Kerala]\n* [http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/322904/Kottayam Britannica Reference on Kottayam]\n* [http://www.mapsofindia.com/maps/kerala/districts/kottayam.htm Kottayam District Map, MapsOfIndia.com]\n\n{{Kottayam|state= expanded}}\n{{Kerala|state= expanded}}\n{{Municipalities of Kerala}}\n{{Kottayam district}}\n{{Central Travancore}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Kottayam district]]\n[[Category:Kottayam| ]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Kottayam district]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|the city in Kerala, India|its namesake district|Kottayam district |the old princely state|Kingdom of Kottayam|the town in northern Kerala|Kottayam-Malabar}}\n{{refimprove|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2016}}\n<!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Indian cities]] for details -->\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Kottayam\n| settlement_type                 = [[City]]\n| image_skyline                   = Purple Swamphen (Porphyrio poliocephalus) 22-Mar-2007 10-12-15 AM.jpg\n| image_alt                       = \n| image_caption                   = Purple Swamphen (''[[Porphyrio porphyrio]]'') photographed in Vembanad Lake, Kottayam\n| native_name_lang                = Malayalam\n'''''Akshara Nagari''''' (Town of Alphabets)<br />\n| pushpin_map                     = India Kerala#India\n| pushpin_label_position          = right\n| pushpin_map_alt                 = \n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location in Kerala, India\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|9.5947087|N|76.4855729|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = India\n| subdivision_type1           