to }}</ref> ||  ||  style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{dts|2019|12|26}} || rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Netflix  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Original Films]] and [[One Race Films]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 36 || ''[[Kipo and the Age of Wonderbeasts]]''<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/trolls-world-tour/ |title=\u2018Trolls 2\u2019 is Officially Titled \u2018Trolls World Tour\u2019; DreamWorks Also Developing \u2018Kipo and the Age of Wonderbeasts\u2019|website=slashfilm.com |date=June 12, 2018|accessdate=June 13, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"SpyRacers2019\"/> || Radford Selchrist<br />Bill Wolkoff || {{Start date|2020|1|14}}<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2019/12/11/netflix-january-2020-new-grace-and-frankie-sabrina/4386946002/|title=Netflix\u2019s January 2020 list: New Seasons of \u2018Grace and Frankie\u2019, \u2018Sabrina\u2019|website=USA Today|first=Carly|last=Mallenbaum}}</ref>||style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Studio Mir]]\n|}\n===Upcoming television series===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=10 | #\n! width=220 | Title\n! width=220 | Creator(s)/Developer(s)\n! width=120 | Premiere date\n! width=200 | Network\n! width=250 | Co-production with\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 37 || ''[[Wizards: Tales of Arcadia]]''<ref name=\"Arcadia\" /> || Guillermo del Toro ||align=center rowspan=\"5\"|{{dts|2020}} || rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Netflix || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Double Dare You Productions\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 38 || ''[[Gabby's Dollhouse]]''<ref name=\"ReferenceD\"/><ref>{{cite web|url= https://kidscreen.com/2019/07/29/spin-master-enters-gabbys-dollhouse/ |title=Spin Master enters Gabby\u2019s Dollhouse|website=Kidscreen |date=July 29, 2019}}</ref> || [[Traci Paige Johnson]]<br>Jennifer Twomey || rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | N/A\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 39 || ''[[Rhyme Ti