ve Box]]\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2000s|2005]]\n| ''[[Madagascar (2005 film)|Madagascar]]''\n| [[Eric Darnell]] and [[Tom McGrath (animator)|Tom McGrath]]\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2000s|2006]]\n| ''[[Over the Hedge (film)|Over the Hedge]]''\n| [[Tim Johnson (film director)|Tim Johnson]] and [[Karey Kirkpatrick]]\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2000s|2006]]\n| ''[[Flushed Away]]''\n| [[Sam Fell]] and [[David Bowers (director)|David Bowers]]\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2000s|2007]]\n| ''[[Shrek the Third]]''\n| [[Chris Miller (animator)|Chris Miller]] and [[Raman Hui]]\n|-\n| rowspan=3| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2000s|2008]]\n| ''[[Kung Fu Panda]]''\n| [[Mark Osborne (filmmaker)|Mark Osborne]] and [[John Stevenson (director)|John Stevenson]]\n|-\n| ''[[Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa|Madagascar 2: Escape to Africa]]''\n| [[Eric Darnell]] and [[Tom McGrath (animator)|Tom McGrath]]\n|-\n| ''[[Monsters vs Aliens]]''\n| [[Rob Letterman]] and [[Conrad Vernon]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2010s|2010]]\n| ''[[How to Train Your Dragon (film)|How to Train Your Dragon]]''\n| [[Chris Sanders (director)|Chris Sanders]] and [[Dean DeBlois]]\n| rowspan=2 {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2010s|2011]]\n| ''[[Kung Fu Panda 2]]''\n| [[Jennifer Yuh Nelson]]\n|-\n| ''[[Puss in Boots (2011 film)|Puss in Boots]]''\n| [[Chris Miller (animator)|Chris Miller]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2010s|2014]]\n| ''[[How to Train Your Dragon 2]]''\n| [[Dean DeBlois]] and [[Bonnie Arnold]]\n| rowspan=3 {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2010s|2015]]\n| ''[[Kung Fu Panda 3]]''\n| [[Jennifer Yuh Nelson]], [[Alessandro Carloni]] and Melissa Cobb\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Animated Film#2010s|2016]]\n|''[[Trolls (film)|Trolls]]''\n| [[Mike Mitchell (director)|Mike Mitchell]] and   [[Gina Shay]]\n|}\n\n==See also